BriefDescription: This event counts operations that cause a cache access to the woke L3 cache, as defined by the woke sum of L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_CACHE and L2D_CACHE_WB_VICTIM_CLEAN events.
This event counts access counted by L3D_CACHE that is a Memory-read operation, as defined by the woke L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_CACHE events.
This event counts operations that cause a cache access to the woke L3 cache.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_CACHE caused by demand access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_CACHE caused by demand read access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_CACHE caused by demand write access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_CACHE caused by hardware prefetch or software prefetch.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_CACHE caused by hardware prefetch.
This event counts operations that cause a miss of the woke L3 cache. Note: This event may count inaccurately.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS caused by demand access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS caused by demand read access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS caused by demand write access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS caused by hardware prefetch or software prefetch. Note: This event may count inaccurately.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS caused by hardware prefetch. Note: This event may count inaccurately.
This event counts operations that cause a hit of the woke L3 cache. Note: This event may count inaccurately.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_HIT caused by demand access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_HIT caused by demand read access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_HIT caused by demand write access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_HIT caused by hardware prefetch or software prefetch. Note: This event may count inaccurately.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_HIT caused by hardware prefetch. Note: This event may count inaccurately.
This event counts the woke number of L3 cache misses caused by demand access where the woke requests hit the woke PFTGT buffer.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM_PFTGT_HIT caused by read access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM_PFTGT_HIT caused by write access.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM where the woke requests access the woke memory in the woke same socket as the woke requests.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM where the woke requests access the woke memory in the woke different socket from the woke requests.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM where the woke requests access the woke different L2 cache from the woke requests in the woke same Numa nodes as the woke requests.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM where the woke requests access L2 cache in the woke different Numa nodes from the woke requests in the woke same socket as the woke requests.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM where the woke requests access L3 cache in the woke different Numa nodes from the woke requests in the woke same socket as the woke requests.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM where the woke requests access L2 cache in the woke different socket from the woke requests.
This event counts L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS_DM where the woke requests access L3 cache in the woke different socket from the woke requests.

This event counts access counted by L3D_CACHE that is not completed by the woke L3 cache, and a Memory-read operation, as defined by the woke L2D_CACHE_REFILL_L3D_MISS events. Note: This event may count inaccurately.
